data.description: Great opportunity for this 1 STORY 4-2-2 ~ Open Living, Dining & large Kitchen with Breakfast Bar, Stainless Steel Appliances, Granite Countertops, tiled backsplash & Walk-in Pantry ~ Private Primary Bedroom, Garden Tub, Separate Shower & big W-I Closet with built-ins ~ Wood like tile throughout with carpet in bedrooms! ~ Home is Connected Smart Home Technology, 15 SEER HVAC Heat Pump System, Garage Door Opener, 6 ft privacy fenced backyard & Sprinkler System! ~ Surround Sound in Living & Back patio for entertaining! ~ 4th bdrm is currently being used as office but is a dedicated 4th bdrm per builder plan ~ Convenient to I-35W, HWY 1187,Burleson, Shops, Dining, Hospital & much more!
